reviewText: So much cheaper than the Baby First website and my daughter loves these shows.
My baby girl loves Peek-a-Boo from BabyFirst TV. It's her favorite character. Very happy with it.
its great
Two year old loves it.
20 month old daughter loves this!
Boring, even for babies.

A new grandchild we babysit prompted me to purchase this video. I believe that it will be enjoyed based upon the many positive reviews on Amazon. My wife and I watched about half and can see where this video will be well received by our new addition.

Too many of our children videos are geared for our older grandchild so I desired to have this one for the new child. At the price this is worth acquiring if you have - or antisipate having - very young children in your home.
Bought this for a road trip that we took and the kids had no problem watching this over and over again. They are both big peek-a-boo fans.
Love it
Great price, but one can only watch so much peekaboo....wish there was commercials, lol.
Cute
Love it!  Happy tots
My twins looooovvvvveeeeeeeee Peek a boo!
Grandchild loves.
Baby's favorite game is Peek-a Boo.  She loves to watch the video.
Our twin girls love this video. It's one of their favorite shows on the baby first channel.
awesome
Arrived in a timely manner & my daughter loves it.

I bought this for my 9 month old nephew. He loves this show! I imagine that the quality of this DVD is good because my brother has commented that my nephew watches it every day. I have video of my nephew laughing every time that little blue creature pops out and says, Peek-a-boo. Wish I could upload it.
Our Grand daughter loves all these shows. It was a wonderful Christmas surprise for her and her parents. Makes her car travels much more pleasant for mommy too!
Quick delivery, purchased as a gift for my nephew who loves this program on Baby First.
My sons love this show! Extremely cute! I have a 6year old with autism  he doesn't  speak yet but he sings the peek a boo song!  To get me to press play on his movie

My daughter loves this dvd! She loved watching the show on TV but it did not come on very often so I bought the dvd. She watches it all the time and is always giggling about it. Peek-A-Boo is her BFF! Even my 2 year old son enjoys it.
My great granddaughter loves this DVD. She loves the characters on the Baby First Station.
Kid has watched this approximately 1 million times. Age 1 to 2 suggested. The sound effects seem to be what the kid really likes.
The baby loves it....so I love it!!!
My infant loves his peen a boo dvd
Havent had chance to review it . But not good at all !!! It was scratch and pausing a lot doesnt matter which DVD player I use or computer.
My daughter has loved this video since she was 9 months old. A year later, and she still gets excited when Peek a Boo comes on.
Purchased along with Peek a Boo Baby for a little one year old and she loves it!  Sherry
Received broken

I love that this has a longer run time than other babyfirst videos. I can do a couple  chores while my toddler is entertained. Every parent needs a little  time without a kid shadowing their every move. Then when I'm done with my chore I sit and sing  along and pretend with my baby along with the video.

My baby boy loves baby first tv cartoons and shows. These shows are perfect for baby's to interact with and unlike other cartoons these seem to keep baby calm. Also I got this DVD for a really good price on Amazon! Great for car rides!
